singing voices from your daddy.

03:13.368 --> 03:15.234
He used to sing
in his church choir

03:15.236 --> 03:16.735
just like you two.

03:16.737 --> 03:18.369
We're hoping
for bigger audiences

03:18.371 --> 03:19.872
than Methodists, Meemaw.

03:19.874 --> 03:23.543
